description: Monday, 5 January: Rakib and Raihan Hossain Rana-two activists of pro-BNP Jatiyatabadi Chhatra Dal (JCD)-were shot dead and 15 others injured during a clash with Awami League workers at Tebaria in Natore district town in the morning
